So until Mr Cameron gets round to approving an HD master for release this is all we've got.

This was ripped 'anomorphic strict' to preserve the full resolution of the disc, I've watched on my 44&quot; screen and it really does look much better than region 1 &amp; 2 versions, especially the underwater stuff which looks great.

